"
    }
   },
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "<!-- ![Screenshot 2025-06-23 at 11.46.52.png](attachment:55e196a3-2d42-469c-8b7d-938a56b47f38.png) -->\n",
    "<img\n",
